                NodeIDType reconfiguratorID,

                int startingPortNumber,
                long pingLatency,
                double latitude,
                double longitude)
        *********************************************************** Constructs a NameServerInfo with the give parameter
        Parameters:
        id - Name server id
        activeReplicaID - id of the activeReplica part of the name server.
        reconfiguratorID - id of the reconfigurator part of the name server
        ipAddressString - ip address as a string
        externalIP -
        startingPortNumber - first port number of block of ports used for TCP and UDP comms
        pingLatency - RTT latency between the local nameserver and this nameserver in milleseconds
        latitude - Latitude of the nameserver
        longitude - Longitude of the nameserver
